edback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oai1665702671540.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oai1665702671540.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oai1665702671540.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oai1665702671540\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the application icon to be used when the application (or session panel) is\n    minimized. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface\n    IDE.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"oai1665702671540__topic_d144416e1_d144417e1_d144418e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oai1665702671540__p_d144419e1_d144420e1_d144421e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Icon</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oai1665702671540__section_pgd_jgc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1240281e65\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oai1665702671540__p_d144425e1_d144426e1_d144427e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FileName</var>—name of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ico</span> file</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"oai1665702671540__table_d17528e1_d17529e1_d17530e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ila1665702671184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ila1665702671184.html\" title=\"The [application] section of the initialization file enables you to set application-level defaults for a Windows desktop application.\">[application]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oai1665702671540__section_p5s_tjc_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1240281e118\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">This setting has no effect on the icon displayed in the application shortcut. To change the\n        icon in the shortcut, edit its properties and choose another image.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530500\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530500\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Icon Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the application icon to be used when the application (or session panel) is minimized. This setting applies only to the Uniface runtime on Windows, not to the Uniface IDE. Icon = FileName Arguments FileName —name of the .ico file Default value: None File section: [application] Description This setting has no effect on the icon displayed in the application shortcut. To change the icon in the shortcut, edit its properties and choose another image. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}